{
  "stem": "19837.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And during the day, he worked at everything and anything he could lay his hand on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One time he stood on the street 4, 5 o'clock in the morning and sold bread or-- for us, for the refugees-- from a bakery.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had our own bakeries, our own butcher shops, our own restaurants.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- but all that didn't give us a living.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went with him then, as a waitress and worked a little bit until we had to move into the-- what they called district.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Japanese walked in in 1943 and sent all of us, 18,000 or 20,000, into a certain part of Shanghai, where we already lived.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hongkew.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the people-- a few people, not too many-- lived outside of this district.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The people who had jobs or could make a living without help, not like us, they had to move back where we were.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had to move in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, what I found out now is that the Germans wanted the Japanese to do the same with us what they did in Germany, but the Japanese refused.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All they did was put us in a district.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, if we already had a little job, like my husband, and me, too, we had to go to the police and get a passport to leave the district.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a Japanese called [NON-ENGLISH] who, who said he's-- who called himself the King of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was absolutely crazy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He just did what he wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Either he loved you or he hated you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He slapped a few people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had to stand up on the table to reach some of the men, because he was also very short.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
